{"id":"ecee17ae-7130-4685-beca-26396283ba6a","name":"Johanna - Religious Studies professor (Fate/Grand Order College AU)","description":"<p>Midterms are over. You survived Konstantinos's tests. Now, taking a walk to relax, you stumble upon Johanna, the Religious Studies professor, singing to herself in one of the campus park's benches.</p><p></p><h3><strong>Vibes:</strong></h3><p><strong>Song:</strong> <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/6GuAb6sS3v0KWNsdvf2kX5?si=0db5a5127ba64189\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>\"Viva La Vida\"</em> (Bossa Nova ver.)</a> – <em>for the fallen pope aesthetic. Seriously, listen to this. It's so good. This is my headcanon voice claim for english speaking Johanna.</em></p><p>A corkboard of \"debunked\" saints with her face added in Sharpie</p><p>The scent of incense and gunpowder (from <em>\"experimental liturgy\"</em>)</p><p><strong>A sticky note on her door:</strong> <em>\"Ye Without Sin Can Suck It\"</em></p><p></p><p>Current bots in the Chaldea University series:</p><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/bc72ca19-9594-4fab-9613-1718472a3df4_character-konstantinos-xi-history-teacher-fate-grand-order-college-au\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Konstantinos - History Professor (Rooftop conversation)</a></p><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/96b8bb45-f919-4d03-ad4f-afcddc172af0_character-asterios-veterinary-medicine-student-fate-grand-order-college-au\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Asterios - Veterinary Medicine student (Helping at his farm)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/af4d91ae-ab56-4d0a-b394-d26882d66ef8_character-circe-veterinary-medicine-professor-fate-grand-order-college-au\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Circe - Veterinary Medicine teacher (Helping her out)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/dc705fe0-89ed-4e08-ab26-146ad5671c08_character-habetrot-shopping-trip-fate-grand-order-college-au\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Habbycat - Fashion Design student (Shopping Trip)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/bd74a846-45df-4bb9-8134-394a5be0bec9_character-medea-performing-arts-professor-fate-grand-order-college-au\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Medea - Theater Professor (Caught in the act)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/65bb23be-2837-4c64-85e5-35ec443b5cea_character-senji-muramasa-materials-science-professor-fate-grand-order-college-au\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Muramasa - Materials Science professor (Post-injury check-up)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/bbda1711-bf75-4699-919f-1ae9fea516ee_character-professor-morgan-le-faye-fate-grand-order-college-au\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Morgan - Fashion Design professor (Graduation offer)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6c559753-491f-428d-a00b-b9b1bf04c899_character-ereshkigal-anthropology-professor-fate-grand-order-college-au\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Ereshkigal - Anthropology teacher (Field trip)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/78a2314a-d98a-445a-9cd1-7fbad57bd893_character-ishtar-art-history-professor-fate-grand-order-college-au\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Ishtar - Art History (Museum trip)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/d240f4f0-d64d-4406-b969-ff0a8413f543_character-baobhan-sith-college-au-toxic-lover-fate-grand-order\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Baobhan Sith - Toxic Lover (Fashion Design major)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/16aec8e0-38ae-430b-a8af-b6dad75fe59b_character-melusine-barghest-college-au-party-